transcript.text: Hello, welcome to on Print Shop.
This video is about photo print which is an add on.

This product allow customers to build their photos in the print photo builder screen, apply additional options, order the same photo with multiple sizes in multiple quantities, then can add borders, orientation, crop and apply many more effects.
We are introducing a print builder screen where customers can upload their images from the upload photos button.
Let's see how this product looks at customer and and after that we will see how to set up in admin.
The front page will look like this where it need to be.
Click on proceed to next step.
Here you can import as many photos as you want.
This screen is termed as Print Photo builder.
Here all photos will look like this.
Here are multiple options available like you can crop image, create border and many more effects to the image.
Also you can change quantity, additional option, alter size, duplicate same photo in other size and many more summary will be visible like this.
Click on continue checkout.
The cart will look like this where size and additional options will be visible with number of prints.
By clicking on view products button you can see all your photos.
All the photos will be visible with image quantity and additional option.
Let's see how to set this product in admin.
All the things will remain same as normal product.
You need to select photo print from product type.
Here The price defining method is only one which is range based with multiplication and there is only one action button which is custom design.

The next thing need to be taken care in additional option where you have to create one additional option group as export order data group name as photo prints and assign all additional option under this group.
It is also mentioned here.
Once the order will be placed it will be visible like this in admin.
If you have any queries please contact us at support@onprintshop.com.
Thank you.
